#X text 50 220 In order to make a connection in the Edit mode \, first
go to an outlet and see when the mouse cursor becomes a circle \, now
you can click and drag to create a connection cord and take it into
an inlet and release the mouse button. Connections are also made from
an Outlet to an Inlet. To disconnect \, go to a cord and click when
the cursor becomes an "X" to select it \, then hit backspace/delete.
